    <h2 class="mt-5 text-[24px] font-semibold">What's next</h2>
    <p class="mt-4">From April 2024, we will begin rolling out Caddy as a randomised controlled trial with two local Citizens Advice centres in Greater Manchester. Building on learnings from the prototype built and tested in CASORT last year, we will use our evaluation to gain valuable insights into how Caddy could be effectively and responsibly deployed across public services, prioritising safety and effectiveness. Following this initial phase, we will seek partners interested in exploring wider applications of this technology.</p>
    <p class="mb-2 mt-4">You can find our code on Github at <a class="link" href="https://github.com/i-dot-ai/caddy-chatbot">https://github.com/i-dot-ai/caddy-chatbot</a>. We welcome any contributions for the project and encourage experimentation!</p>

